      "widgets_values": [
        "### 11 AnyFast — Upload Image as Asset, use as First Frame\nLoad an image → SeedanceUploadAsset (creates group + uploads to AnyFast asset storage) → SeedanceAssetRef (wraps the asset:// ID into ANYFAST_IMAGE_REFS with role=first_frame) → Seedance2 via anyfast_refs.\nThe asset is stored persistently on AnyFast — save the group_id output to reuse it across runs without re-uploading."
